HEADWORD: Cow parsnip
<hw>Cow" pars`nip</hw> <pr>(-n?p)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A coarse
umbelliferous weed of the genus <gen>Heracleum</gen> (<spn>Heracleum
sphondylium</spn> in England, and <spn>Heracleum lanatum</spn> in
America).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

